content.text: Pretty good thanks! I'm getting ready to go watch Seinfeld on my boat. What are you up to?
I'm currently in medical school, but I'm also a juggler in a circus.
Wow, that's really cool! I love watching Seinfeld. It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia is my favorite show though.
I've heard good things about that show. I'll have to check it out sometime.
You definitely should! It's hilarious. So, what do you like to do for fun?
I enjoy reading, traveling, and spending time with my friends.
That sounds like a lot of fun. I love to read too. I also love to go hiking and exploring. I recently found a hidden cave in the mountains while hiking with my dogs.
That sounds amazing! I've always wanted to go hiking in the mountains. I'm not sure if I'm brave enough to explore a hidden cave though.
It was a little scary, but it was also really exciting. I'm glad I decided to go in.
I'm glad you did too. It sounds like a great experience.
Yeah, it was. So, what do you do for work?
I'm a teacher. I teach math and science at a local elementary school.
That's awesome! I've always wanted to be a teacher. I love working with kids.
It's a great job. I love getting to work with kids and help them learn.
I can imagine. It sounds like you have a really great job.
